IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Bridgett Marie WOOD and Clinton Andrew Wood Upon the Petition of Bridgett Marie Wood, Petitioner-Appellee, And Concerning Clinton Andrew Wood, n/k/a Clinton Andrew Lunden, Respondent-Appellant. No. 18-0454 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed February 6, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Clinton Lunden appeals the physical care, visitation, and child support provisions of the decree dissolving his marriage to Bridgett Wood. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED.

AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED.
